headline: MODS ACTIVE
subtitle: GTACashLobbyTutorial's mod server is active
content:
You are currently using a GTA Online mod server set up using http://reddit.com/user/GTACashLobbyTutorial's tutorial. (http://redd.it/1t84sg)

Many things are majorly discounted. Buying them with the discount might be harder to detect than hacking large sums of cash. If you want to get rid of large amounts of cash, buy bicycles. Make sure to deposit the cash into your bank account first.
